<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>As discussed on #zftalk, we need to do the following with Zend_Form_Element:</p>

<ul><li>If an element is required and does not contain a NotEmpty validator, add one to the top of the validator stack with the breakChainOnFailure flag set to true</li>
<li>Add a flag and accessors that allow disabling the above behaviour on request.</li>
</ul><p>This will enforce the semantic meaning of the required flag.</p>

